name: Visitors: Chalice
description:
11"x14"
Limited Edition of 50
Signed & Numbered
Archival Glossy Paper
Printed edge to edge, no border

These are high quality digital photographs of absolutely unique handcrafted, kinetic glass and neon sculptures by artist Rick Zar. Neither the color or content have been manipulated in any way. Each of these sculptures is approximately 4 feet tall by 3 feet wide and are disassembled permanently after each photo shoot, making these images completely one of a kind.
